{
  "stem": "1363.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I always had to work very, very hard for my living and for the children's living.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I learned dressmaking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, eventually, I had my own clothing factory.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I did do some RR work, where I was very happy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember that, when I separated, and my husband-- my husband said that I'm going to break the bank, sort of, meaning that I won't be able to survive it on my own with the children, on my own salary.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That I'm going to go bankrupt.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, I didn't, but that's besides the point.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I brought up those two boys financially, right through till they became 18 years of age, where they helped a little bit to it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I always had the feeling, proud feeling, that these kids, I did a good job.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They brought-- they were brought up-- one was born in 1960, the other in '64, for they're now around the age where it was very hard to bring up two boys on your own, with a working mother.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it-- they're not dropouts.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They're educated.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They are not bludgers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They work.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They are not drug addicts.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I feel that I did a good job, as much as I did.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Even with religion, they do feel Jewish to the very day, even they're out of the Jewish home.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just been born about six, eight months ago.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I'm very happy with them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm very proud Yiddish grandmother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have flashbacks.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have dreams.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But, funny enough, nothing to do with the war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It is dreams, and I don't know, is it my medication which I am under, that I have every night.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Something-- it's not unpleasant dreams.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
